### KEY CONCLUSIONS
1. TV470 (v863) budget changes alone = BEST variant (11.42 4v4 vs lstm, 14.60 6v2 vs Paz)
2. Adding recovery mode (TV471/472) = HURTS
3. Adding capture scramble (TV475/v870) = HURTS 6v2
4. Adding lower thresholds (TV476/v871) = HURTS 6v2 vs mammet
5. All modifications to the proven TV350 budget/behavior tend to hurt on average
6. v716 (TV350) 15.05 average remains very hard to beat
7. Budget-only changes (TV470) help some matchups but likely hurt average

